ve an appointment."},{"content":"The user also provides the appointment identifier that they want to remove.","pos":[15042,15117]},{"content":"This identifier was returned from <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>AppointmentManager.ShowAddAppointmentAsync<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/Dn297221manager-showaddappointmentasync)</ept>.","pos":[15118,15290],"source":" This identifier was returned from [**AppointmentManager.ShowAddAppointmentAsync**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/Dn297221manager-showaddappointmentasync)."},{"content":"If the user clicked <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Delete<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, the sample prints that it removed the appointment specified by that appointment identifier.","pos":[15291,15414],"source":" If the user clicked **Delete**, the sample prints that it removed the appointment specified by that appointment identifier."},{"content":"Show a time span for the appointments provider","pos":[17397,17443]},{"content":"Call the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>AppointmentManager.ShowTimeFrameAsync<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/Dn297221manager-showtimeframeasync)</ept> method to show a specific time span for the default appointments provider's primary UI if the user clicked <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Show<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>.","pos":[17445,17698],"source":"Call the [**AppointmentManager.ShowTimeFrameAsync**](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/apps/Dn297221manager-showtimeframeasync) method to show a specific time span for the default appointments provider's primary UI if the user clicked **Show**."},{"content":"The sample prints that the default appointments provider appeared on screen.","pos":[17699,17775]},{"content":"Create an appointment-recurrence object and apply data to it","pos":[18209,18269]},{"content":"Create an <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Windows.ApplicationModel